                        <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A4e/579: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">American Delegation</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-04-28T18:00:00-04:00"><hi rend="italic">April 28,
                                        1926—6 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>20. I approve attitude outlined in paragraph 2 of your telegram number 33
                            of April 26, 6 p.m.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi></signed></closer>
